<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑商法，先用一个较合适的数作试商（未确定的商），如接近于整十、整百......，然后乘以除数，得积与被除数对比，看是大还是小，经调整后得确商（已确定不变的商），定下商数。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">3465÷35=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 2170÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=(2100+70)÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2100÷35+70÷35</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60+2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=62</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>